subject: PLDM: Implement SetFruRecordTable and CM
commitMessage:
PLDM: Implement SetFruRecordTable and CM

This commit implements the setFruRecordTable command
and also updates the DBus property for the cable cards
for which the host sends a setFrurecordTable command.

Tested: using pldmtool

Signed-off-by: Pavithra Barithaya <pavithra.b@ibm.com>
Change-Id: I70e4f85f627577d8ca1bc90447b10e9e2e8e7ccd
